Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.21,0:00:25.39,We Are Remix lyrics,,0,0,0,,em busca dos nossos desejos... O One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.49,0:00:32.69,We Are Remix lyrics,,0,0,0,,Bússolas só nos atrasam...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.99,0:00:38.75,We Are Remix lyrics,,0,0,0,,Cheio de ânimo, eu tomo o leme!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.87,0:00:43.74,We Are Remix lyrics,,0,0,0,,Se provarmos que este mapa empoeirado é verdadeiro,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.07,0:00:48.88,We Are Remix lyrics,,0,0,0,,seu tesouro não será mais uma lenda!
